| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2025-6494 — Recovery Inhibition (termite)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: dc8c567c-fad3-5f8c-bfb7-ad2e644fa16b"
